pyhton OS file and dir methods

to run a file as a new process
import os
os.system('python my_file.py')

to show the current working directory
import os
os.getcwd()

to change current working directory
import os
os.chdir('c:/users')

to list directories and files in current working directory
import os
os.listdir()

to create a directory
import os
os.mkdir('dir_name')
